State - if this object is Active, Inactive or Deleted
ControlGroup - how this object is located in the Repository; Managed. External, Inline or Referenced
String - Mime type
String - Date when the datastream was created
String - Label
boolean - whether updates to this object will over right the original or if a new version will be created
